data.description: Under Construction. Under construction. The spacious and open concept, two-story Seamist Home with 2-car garage is brand new, energy efficient, and features a den with French doors upgrade as well as a tub upgrade in the Master Bath. This home will be available early April in the high demand area of Wesley Chapel, in Epperson, the country's first Crystal Lagoon community! Come enjoy lagoon life with beaches, tiki bars, water slides, cabana pools, and kayak rentals... all just steps from outside your front door!  This home will show you what open concept is all about from the second you enter through the front door and into the welcoming foyer which leads to the oversized gathering room, dining room and kitchen all opened up together. This large and luxurious entertaining space features a set of slider glass doors off the kitchen which lead out to an open patio that is perfect for where you can sit back, relax, and enjoy the outdoors all year round. The kitchen features 36" and 42" maple cabinets with crown molding, granite countertops, and under cabinet lighting. Upstairs you will find a huge loft area along with the Owner's Suite and secondary bedrooms. The laundry room is conveniently located on the second floor as well for easy accessibility from the bedroom. This home is brand new and quality construction. The Crystal Lagoon is now open! Welcome home to the Seamist at Epperson! Please note that similar model pictures shown are for illustration purposes only. Elevations, colors and options may vary.
